title: Dry Aged Ribeye vs Wet Aged Ribeye Steak
description:
Also see my followup video regarding dry aging: 
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7iQwPFmCTbQ

A detailed video about how to Dry Age Ribeye using UMAi Dry Steak Bags (28 days). At the end, I compare the taste & tenderness of dry aged choice vs wet aged prime ribeye. I must say, the dry aged won. Prime steaks are great, but do not compare to dry aged steak. This was a video requested by YouTube user haftafish8780.
http://www.drybagsteak.com/
http://www.youtube.com/user/haftafish8780
